  "text": "Specially, clonal integration distinctly increased the PLFAs concentration of ECM fungi (18:2v6,9) by 72% (Fig. 3g) . This was consistent with a previous girdling experiment [CITATION_1] . Our results further confirm that the dramatic increase in fungi caused by clonal integration is associated with a increase in C supply and that fungi depend to a much higher degree on belowground C allocation [CITATION_2] .",
